{"tid":409240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"標普將香港評級下調至「AA+」","createTime":"2017-09-22T02:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T09:59:58.000Z","uid":4783,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce6ef9a4af02d85d2a35431aa685b8e0deeb8da","tid":409240,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"標普將香港評級從「AAA」調至「AA+」，展望由「負面」調至「穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n標普周四將中國評級從「AA-」下調至「A+」，展望穩定；稱中國長期強勁的信貸增長增加了中國的經濟和金融風險。標普並下調了中國農業發展銀行、國家開發銀行、中國進出口銀行、星展中國、恒生中國、滙豐中國的評級<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170922/bkn-20170922094612423-0922_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170922%2Fbkn-20170922094612423-0922_00842_001.html&d=qroZlc9dXuMIgrlW3t05I8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=4e257f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170922/bkn-20170922094612423-0922_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名等睇政府班柒頭出黎吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f148682fe907fe7628d5ea24362a60b4dd8495","tid":409240,"uid":98139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:07:01.000Z","msg":"政府發出聲明斥降級缺乏理據、純屬臆測、非常不認同，并重申香港有完善的監管及法律制度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba382bcae1586c3f9cdddae96be2ba7bb4ba34d2","tid":409240,"uid":98139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府發出聲明斥降級缺乏理據、純屬臆測、非常不認同，并重申香港有完善的監管及法律制度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留名等睇咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1f367b5f80a465d94c818b63a1b500f002e57b","tid":409240,"uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:10:34.000Z","msg":"中央送